title: PioneersProductions Live Show Audio Recording June 14, 2014
description:
This is PioneersProductions' live show from yesterday/today (started 06-14-14; ended 06-15-14). The reason he went live today was because he tweeted about possibly quitting YouTube in about a year.

Unfortunately you can't see the comments that were left in the chat during the show, and Randy doesn't acknowledge most of them, but they were really supportive and made me proud to be part of this community.

Live the previous audio recordings, this is named "Google Chrome" because that's what the audio was ripped from.

This show started out really moody (and ended that way, too...) but somewhere towards the end of the middle section it got kinda funny and optimistic just like a usual broadcast.

Total time: 3 hours 30 minutes 13 seconds.

The audio in the beginning is a bit laggy, and towards the end I actually lost connection to the chat, causing Randy to almost end the show early. I had to refresh the page to get the chat to work again, but you didn't miss much.

Enjoy!

Sincerely,
The PioneersProductions Archivist
 - imatu -
